The Siege Tee design is an extravagant all over luxury design, very detailed in composition featuring gold zippers on the left side, right side, and collar 

This design is limited edition, which means a limited quantity will be manufactured. This is one of the more exclusive designs  PALAIS PVRIS will release.

we will be releasing a total of 100 shirts with this design,
